name: Leigong
shortLoreBlurb: Leigong is a deity from China tied to thunder duke, justice. Myths connect them with tempests and rulership.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Indra (Vedic), Karttikeya (Hindu), Perun (Slavic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Thor (Norse), Zeus (Greek)
